            . I am a plaisterer, and live next door to Bartlett. I saw the prisoner in Cecil-court with this bedstead, and Mrs. Bartlett following him; she desired me to stop him, which I did; he said a man gave him 1 s. to carry it - that he did not know where the man was. I told him to take it back to where he brought it from; he took it to Bartlett's shop.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
